  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Suzaku Clan, level 8+, Midas Touch Clan Feat</p><p>You have rekindled your family's lost spark gaining absolute control of your flames like never before.</p><ul><li>Whenever you would deal fire damage to an allied creature, the allied creature instead is unaffected from the source as your tempered flames harmlessly wash over them. You may use this on a number of creatures equal to your proficiency bonus per instance of fire damage.</li><li>Jutsu you use with the Fire Release keyword has its healing amount increased by an amount equal to 1 + your proficiency bonus.</li><li>Whenever you use medical ninjutsu with the fire release keyword on another creature, your soothing flames rejuvenate the creature(s) allowing them to roll a number of Chakra die equal to the Rank of the jutsu cast restoring chakra equal to the result. (D-Rank: 1, C-Rank: 2, B-Rank: 3, A-Rank: 4, S-Rank: 5). You can only use this feature once per long rest.</li></ul>",
